videos.description: With the shot clock at three seconds, Baylor's Davion Mitchell inbounds the ball and gets it right back to knock down the jump shot as the buzzer sounds.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Mitchell's jumper beats the shot clock for Baylor) 2020/01/20

videos.headline: Mitchell's jumper beats the shot clock for Baylor

videos.description: Baylor's Devonte Bandoo knocks down the transition 3-pointer getting the Baylor crowd on their feet.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Bandoo's 3 gets the Baylor crowd on their feet) 2020/01/20

videos.headline: Bandoo's 3 gets the Baylor crowd on their feet

videos.description: Baylor turns the ball over and Oklahoma guard Austin Reaves has a chance to give the Sooners the lead but is unable to knock down the 3-pointer.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Oklahoma’s Reaves misses potential game-winning 3) 2020/01/20 ESHEET

videos.headline: Oklahoma's Reaves misses potential game-winning 3
